!----------WARNING----------------!
This program works correctly and has been tested on Windows and
Linux, but only on the latter are setted up the function of
saving and loading game.
Opening the "Scacchi_main.c" file, at line 21, you can change "debuggo" to 1
to activate debug (verbose) mode
!---------------------------------!


